1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,011
Put these five procedures to work for you.

2
00:00:03,011 --> 00:00:04,050
1.

3
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:06,291
Action cures fear.

4
00:00:06,640 --> 00:00:10,130
Isolate your fear and then take constructive action.

5
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:16,530
Inaction, doing nothing about a situation, strengthens fear and destroys confidence.

6
00:00:16,530 --> 00:00:18,050
2.

7
00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:23,090
Make a supreme effort to put only positive thoughts in your memory bank.

8
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:28,291
Don't let negative, self-deprecatory thoughts grow into mental monsters.

9
00:00:28,560 --> 00:00:32,931
Simply refuse to recall unpleasant events or situations.

10
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:37,491
Three, put people in proper perspective.

11
00:00:37,681 --> 00:00:42,530
Remember, people are more alike, much more alike than they are different.

12
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:45,251
Get a balanced view of the other fellow.

13
00:00:45,360 --> 00:00:47,650
He is just another human being.

14
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:50,530
And develop an understanding attitude.

15
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:55,011
Many people will bark, but it's a rare one who bites.

16
00:00:56,080 --> 00:01:00,690
Four, practice doing what your conscience tells you is right.

17
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:04,690
This prevents a poisonous guilt complex from developing.

18
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:09,170
Doing what's right is a very practical rule for success.

19
00:01:09,170 --> 00:01:11,011
5.

20
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:16,291
Make everything about you say, I'm confident, really confident.

21
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:20,451
Practice these little techniques in your day-to-day activities.

22
00:01:20,721 --> 00:01:29,011
Be a front-seater, make eye contact, walk 25% faster, speak up, smile big.

